description:
I Love Finding Cats! - Collector's Edition is a classic Hidden Object game with a great selection of mini-games. Visit beautiful locations from across the globe while you find and collect adorable feline friends!

This Collector's Edition also includes Christmas Bonus levels.

- 6 extra locations – find even more cats!
- double zoom feature for Hidden Object scenes
- 12 additional minigames
- Additional adoptable cats
- Meet the developers’ adorable cats
name: I Love Finding Cats! - Collector's Edition
